description: Amundi EUR High Yield Corporate Bond ESG UCITS ETF Acc seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising or falling, the performance of the iBoxx MSCI ESG EUR High Yield Corporates TCA TRI Index (the "Index"), and to minimize the tracking error between the net asset value of the Sub-Fund and the performance of the Index. The anticipated level of tracking error, under normal market conditions, is indicated in the prospectus of the Sub-Fund. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi Euro High Yield Bond ESG UCITS ETF Acc
